title: #237: Nun Of The Above (@KelliDunham)
itunes:title: Nun Of The Above with Kelli Dunham
description: Kelli Dunham met me in a park in Brooklyn to talk about her days as a nun. She, for real, lived in a nunnery and did all that garbage. Can you imagine living like that? Join us for a beautiful day in the park.
